      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Mesh convergence studies performed on representative pedicle screw construct geometry. Peak von Mises stress and construct stiffness converged to within 3% on the production mesh relative to the refined reference mesh."
    },
