      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Direct sparse solvers employed; residual norms monitored and confirmed below 1e-8 for all simulation runs. No iterative solver divergence events recorded."
