      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic continuum model with frictional contact at screw-rod and screw-block interfaces. Model form selected based on prior validation studies and literature consensus for quasi-static ASTM F1717 loading regime."
